    "offset": 288050,
    "slot_size": 260,
    "data_size": 256,
    "nom_orig": "Jun",
    "texte_orig": "My[SP]father[SP]warned[SP]you[SP]that[SP]the[SP]Oracle[SP]of[SP]Maia\nmust[SP]not[SP]be[SP]fulfilled![1205][001E][SP]Father[SP]didn't[SP]wish\nfor[SP]the[SP]world's[SP]annihilation!",
