    "nom_orig": "Ms.[SP]Ideal",
    "texte_orig": "Kashihara's[SP]boy...[1205][001E][SP]Which[SP]means[SP]you're[SP]HER\nson...[1205][001E][SP]Are[SP]you[SP]going[SP]to[SP]slander[SP]your[SP]father\njust[SP]like[SP]she[SP]did!?",
