    "data_size": 260,
    "nom_orig": "Ms.[SP]Ideal",
    "texte_orig": "Your[SP]mother[SP]didn't[SP]understand[SP]Kashihara's\nepochal[SP]research[SP]and[SP]treated[SP]him[SP]with[SP]utter\ncontempt![SP]But[SP]I[SP]knew[SP]better!",
